window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Danger is everywhere. Desire is a constant companion. And Charles? He’s about to face a threat even he can’t charm his way out of.</b></p> <p>He’s not your average mage and when a simple hunt for a relic explodes a temple and tears a hole in reality, he’s framed for the catastrophe.</p> <p>Now, with the Obsidian Order hunting him and ancient mages stirring in the dark, Charles must race to find seven powerful relics. A world-ending rift is unraveling reality, and Charles, armed with a team of wanted women, is the only one who can stop it.</p>"; 
